{"id":13694,"date":"2022-07-26T13:46:01","date_gmt":"2022-07-26T06:46:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=13694"},"modified":"2022-07-26T13:46:02","modified_gmt":"2022-07-26T06:46:02","slug":"hyundai-creta-vuot-kia-seltos-lan-dau-lot-top-10-xe-ban-chay-tai-viet-nam","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-creta-vuot-kia-seltos-lan-dau-lot-top-10-xe-ban-chay-tai-viet-nam\/","title":{"rendered":"Hyundai Creta v\u01b0\u1ee3t Kia Seltos, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ecdt top 10 xe b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"singular-sapo\">M\u1eabu xe g\u1ea7m cao \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb Creta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfm t\u1ef7 tr\u1ecdng cao trong doanh s\u1ed1 xe c\u1ee7a Hyundai, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-creta-vuot-kia-seltos-lan-dau-lot-top-10-xe-ban-chay-tai-viet-nam\/hyundai-creta-kompas-1658076422442\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13695\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13695\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/hyundai-creta-kompas-1658076422442.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"680\" height=\"453\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/hyundai-creta-kompas-1658076422442.webp 680w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/hyundai-creta-kompas-1658076422442-300x200.webp 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf nh\u00f3m B-SUV khi doanh s\u1ed1 Kia Seltos gi\u1ea3m m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n 1.000 chi\u1ebfc, v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c 705 xe giao trong th\u00e1ng 6. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 Hyundai Creta c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3m nh\u01b0ng \u00edt h\u01a1n, duy tr\u00ec \u1edf m\u1ee9c 830 xe, qua \u0111\u00f3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u &#8220;\u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng&#8221;. Doanh s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Creta l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong top 10 xe b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p>T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t linh ki\u1ec7n, khan hi\u1ebfm ngu\u1ed3n cung \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh giao xe v\u00e0 Kia Seltos kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7. M\u1eabu B-SUV n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Thaco l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c &#8220;ch\u00e1y h\u00e0ng&#8221; khi\u1ebfn th\u1eddi gian kh\u00e1ch ch\u1edd giao xe k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 2-3 th\u00e1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Hyundai Creta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u v\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi ri\u00eang Hyundai, doanh s\u1ed1 th\u00e1ng 6 c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y gi\u1ea3m t\u1edbi 34% do thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t linh ki\u1ec7n tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng. Creta v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1eabu xe b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau Hyundai Accent khi k\u00e9m 256 xe.<\/p>\n<p>Trong danh s\u00e1ch 10 xe b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y th\u00e1ng 6, ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe g\u1ea7m cao \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Toyota Corolla Cross, Kia Sonet, Hyundai Creta v\u00e0 Kia Seltos. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o cho th\u1ea5y kh\u00e1ch Vi\u1ec7t ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng chu\u1ed9ng d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y nh\u1edd thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1eaft m\u1eaft, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<\/p>\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n: dantri.com.vn<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<p><span class=\"text\">HYUNDAI H\u1ea2I PH\u00d2NG <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"text\">Hotline kinh doanh: <\/span><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><a class=\"text-is-phone-number\" style=\"color: #ff0000;\">0906.026.299<\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"text\">C\u01a1 s\u1edf 1: 742 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Linh, L\u00ea Ch\u00e2n, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"text\">C\u01a1 s\u1edf 2: 9\/10B L\u00ea H\u1ed3ng Phong, H\u1ea3i An, H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"text\">Youtube: <\/span><a class=\"text-is-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCBBFDZUOt6MMCn158SEzi1w<\/a><\/p>\n<p><span class=\"text\">Facebook: <\/span><a class=\"text-is-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/HyundaiHaiPhong<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u1eabu xe g\u1ea7m cao \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb Creta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfm t\u1ef7 tr\u1ecdng cao trong doanh s\u1ed1 xe c\u1ee7a Hyundai, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf nh\u00f3m B-SUV khi doanh s\u1ed1 Kia Seltos gi\u1ea3m m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13695,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1,30],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13694"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"e